#: apps/log_databus/constants.py:128
msgid ""
"OpenSearch 是一种分布式开源搜索和分析套件，可用于一组广泛的使用案例，如实时应用程序监控、日志分析和网站搜索。OpenSearch "
"提供了一个高度可扩展的系统，通过集成的可视化工具 OpenSearch 控制面板为大量数据提供快速访问和响应，使用户可以轻松地探索他们的数据。与 "
"Elasticsearch 和 Apache Solr 相同的是，OpenSearch 由 Apache Lucene 搜索库提供支持。"
msgstr ""
"OpenSearch is a distributed open source search and analysis suite that can "
"be used for a broad set of use cases, such as real-time application "
"monitoring, log analysis and website search. OpenSearch provides a highly "
"scalable system that provides fast access and response to large amounts of "
"data through an integrated visualization tool, the OpenSearch Dashboard, "
"allowing users to easily explore their data. Like Elasticsearch and Apache "
"Solr, OpenSearch is powered by the Apache Lucene search library."

#: apps/log_databus/constants.py:134
msgid ""
"腾讯云 Elasticsearch Service（ES）是基于开源搜索引擎 Elasticsearch 打造的高可用、可伸缩的云端全托管的 "
"Elasticsearch 服务，包含 Kibana 及常用插件，并集成了安全、SQL、机器学习、告警、监控等高级特性（X-Pack）。使用腾讯云 "
"ES，您可以快速部署、轻松管理、按需扩展您的集群，简化复杂运维操作，快速构建日志分析、异常监控、网站搜索、企业搜索、BI 分析等各类业务。"
msgstr ""
"Tencent Cloud Elasticsearch Service (ES) is a highly available and scalable "
"cloud fully managed Elasticsearch service based on the open source search "
"engine Elasticsearch. It includes Kibana and common plug-ins, and integrates"
" advanced features such as security, SQL, machine learning, alarms, and "
"monitoring. (X-Pack). Using Tencent Cloud ES, you can quickly deploy, easily"
" manage, and expand your clusters on demand, simplify complex operation and "
"maintenance operations, and quickly build various services such as log "
"analysis, exception monitoring, website search, enterprise search, and BI "
"analysis."

#: apps/log_databus/constants.py:140
msgid ""
"Elastic 和 Google Cloud 已建立稳固的合作关系，可以帮助各种规模的企业在 Google Cloud 上部署 Elastic "
"企业搜索、可观测性和安全解决方案，让您能够在数分钟内从数据中获得强大的实时见解。"
msgstr ""
"Elastic and Google Cloud have built a strong partnership to help businesses "
"of all sizes deploy Elastic enterprise search, observability and security "
"solutions on Google Cloud, enabling you to gain powerful real-time insights "
"from your data in minutes ."

